cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.DC 

This paper is about deep learning frameworks and platforms, which are commonly used in machine learning and artificial intelligence research. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision). Additionally, since the paper evaluates the performance of different frameworks and platforms, cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) are also possible sub-categories.
